Field.Description: Selecting this check box turns caching on. If you clear this check box, caching will not take place anywhere this profile is selected. Field.Name: PublishingVaryByRights
Field.Description: Selecting this check box ensures that users must have identical effective permissions on all securable objects to see the same cached page as any other user.

Field.Name: PublishingCacheability

Field.Name: PublishingAuthenticatedUse

Field.Name: PublishingCacheAllowWriters

Field.Description: Selecting this check box bypasses the normal behavior of not allowing people with edit permissions to have their pages cached.
